title: My pixel 4a connects to '19 Toyota no 2way audio. Caller on other end can't hear me?
content:
I've reset BT settings, I have factory reset phone and my car. None worked...

Issue is that my phone connects to my Avalon vida Bluetooth, I can play music, I can read texts, I can even make and receive calls...... But the only issue is that the person on the other end cannot hear me
